title: Farming Simulator 14 v1 2 8 ANDROID
description:
Ever wondered what it's like to live as a tree? Of course you have! Havent we all? Well this game let's you do just that! Feel the wind against your leaves as you experience the action packed life of a tree! The fun is limitless! So what are you waiting for? Get in there and be the best tree you can be!

Start your agricultural career in Farming Simulator 14 on mobile and tablet! Take control of your farm and its fields to fulfil your harvesting dreams.

As well as a refined look and feel, Farming Simulator 14 gives you double the number of farm machines to control, all authentically modelled on equipment from real agricultural manufacturers, including Case IH, Deutz-Fahr, Lamborghini, Kuhn, Amazone and Kron
